ygData.messageBody:
Yeesh i am now cursing the way they did this,
first they force everyone lvl 45 and under out. Then
they make it much harder! so now all the high levels
are convinced that fear plane is too hard. That is
because there isnt enough people now to control the zone.
If they didnt have the lvl block so high i maybee
would have had a chance on some imbued plate *drools* I
hope they change this soon, or atleast fix kedge or
add some high 30s zones. Because those darn lvl 50s
are takin over all the good camp spots. I mean c'mon
i hate hearing it when a druid says "damn it! im
down to 3 haste sashes" HOW FAIR IS THAT!? Oh well i
guess i can dream..<br><br>Kaylin Danmor, lvl 36,
Minstrel of Norrath on the Mithaniel Marr Server
